This NPC is demonstrating a simple dynamic dialog. To make this happen, we:

1. Set his  conversation to "dlg_conv_zoom" (or "dlg_conv_nozoom" if we don't want to zoom in).
2. Add a string variable named "*Dialog" with the value "PoetDialog".
3. Ensure that clicking on the NPC starts his conversation. In this case, we use the "bw_defaultevents" plugin to handle that.
